  "title": "Account Executive",
  "description": "<p>Responsbilities:</p>\n<p>-Handle all types of accounting jobs across diverse industries.</p>\n<p>-Prepare and submit tax return/GST return for clients.</p>\n<p>-Timely preparation of client's accounts and financial reports to avoid late lodgement with ACRA &amp; IRAS etc.</p>\n<p>-Multi-tasking and work independently with self initiative.</p>\n<p>-Liaise with client independently in the course of work</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<p>-Degree/ACCA/Diploma in Accounting</p>\n<p>-1-5 years experiences (Preferably in CPA firm) is a plus</p>\n<p>-Knowledge of Singapore Corporate tax, individual tax and GST</p>\n<p>-Knowledge in MYOB and Xero is a plus</p>\n<p>-Client focused wiht good communication and people skills</p>\n<p>-Systematic, analytical and throught to work with a sense of accountability, integrity and discretion.</p>\n<p>Others:</p>\n<p>-ATTRACTIVE remuneration/ salary to commensurate with experience and competence</p>\n<p>-5 days work week</p>\n<p>-Training will be provided</p>",
